I'll stay here with you for a while.

594
00:19:22,119 --> 00:19:23,880
I'd like to hear your thoughts
for today.

595
00:19:24,359 --> 00:19:25,280
Today,

596
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,680
I just feel like

597
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:30,400
I definitely want to

598
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:32,119
get to know

599
00:19:32,119 --> 00:19:33,280
Zhuoran more.

600
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:35,359
