613
00:20:11,839 --> 00:20:12,959
Any romantic sparks?

614
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:16,160
Hard to say.

615
00:20:16,599 --> 00:20:18,479
I just wanted

616
00:20:18,479 --> 00:20:20,160
