and spend more time together.

617
00:20:24,199 --> 00:20:25,079
Happy for you.

618
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:28,000
Didn't you want to get to know him
from day one?

619
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,680
You know every single thought

620
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:30,800
