621
00:20:31,719 --> 00:20:33,079
You also know my inner thoughts.

622
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:36,839
They just asked how you felt.

623
00:20:37,439 --> 00:20:39,119
I just said she's not feeling well.

624
00:20:39,119 --> 00:20:39,839
I couldn't really

