Okay.

631
00:20:56,599 --> 00:20:57,920
I'm feeling a bit drained.

632
00:20:58,439 --> 00:20:59,040
Are you sleepy?

633
00:20:59,479 --> 00:21:00,520
Why don't you take a quick nap?

634
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:01,920
