635
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,800
Okay, thank you.

636
00:21:21,719 --> 00:21:22,479
Wait for me to come down.

637
00:21:22,479 --> 00:21:23,479
I'll come pick you up.

638
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:25,199
Thank you.

639
