Lie down.

652
00:21:57,839 --> 00:21:58,319
Okay.

653
00:21:59,439 --> 00:22:00,439
Take it slow.

654
00:22:02,040 --> 00:22:03,079
Be careful.

655
00:22:03,760 --> 00:22:04,160
Your bottom.

656
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,520
Yes, sit your bottom down first.

657
00:22:06,359 --> 00:22:07,000
Watch your head.

658
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,079
Your head.

659
00:22:08,079 --> 00:22:08,680
Be careful.

660
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:35,920
About five minutes.

