665
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,119
This foot first.

666
00:22:44,119 --> 00:22:45,040
Still the left foot.

667
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:46,599
Yes, land on your left foot first.

668
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:49,560
