669
00:22:54,239 --> 00:22:55,400
Okay, take it slow.

670
00:22:57,520 --> 00:22:57,959
Okay.

671
00:22:58,959 --> 00:23:00,160
About five minutes.

672
00:23:01,280 --> 00:23:02,560
Don't leave behind your phone and stuff.

673
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,800
Your report has not been reviewed yet.

674
00:23:08,560 --> 00:23:09,520
