676
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:15,599
Please collect it at the bottom right.

677
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:17,359
Your report is ready.

678
00:23:17,359 --> 00:23:18,560
Please collect it at the bottom right.

679
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:19,239
Normal.

680
00:23:19,239 --> 00:23:20,280
It's fine.

681
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:21,079
Nothing's wrong.

682
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,599
Okay.

683
00:23:22,599 --> 00:23:23,640
So we can

684
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,400
