687
00:23:28,760 --> 00:23:29,520
Go home.

688
00:23:31,439 --> 00:23:32,520
Nothing's wrong.

689
00:23:32,520 --> 00:23:33,079
Yes.

690
00:23:33,719 --> 00:23:34,239
You hold this first.

691
00:23:35,599 --> 00:23:36,239
Just to confirm.

692
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:41,520
Just to confirm.

693
00:23:41,520 --> 00:23:42,400
Is it this way?

694
00:23:44,199 --> 00:23:45,319
Go to the consultation room.

695
00:23:45,319 --> 00:23:46,199
